entries.s_10: Oh yeah? That fool got himself lost down in Station Gamma out in Ord Mantell. What do I have to do with it?
entries.s_12: You told him to go there. I have proof.
entries.s_14: Look. You had better leave right now.
entries.s_16: I'll leave... and turn you in to the Car'das.
entries.s_20: What do you want? Can't you see I'm trying to enjoy a drink here!
entries.s_5: What do you want? Do I recognize you? Nah. Must be my imagination. Get lost!
entries.s_6: What? Stop staring at me. I don't want my evening ruined by your antics.
entries.s_9: I know what happened to E'ioua.
